name: Aerials - System of a Down
description:
The second piece from the AI-generated collection based on bands, their music names, and/or lyrics.

"Aerials in the sky
When you lose small mind, you free your life
Aerials, so up high
When you free your eyes, eternal prize"

Since the dawn of time, men have looked at birds and the sky and yearned to fly. The ultimate freedom...
